    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's ready to hit the road! This vehicle is in fair condition and makes for a fantastic, budget-friendly daily driver. While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a sturdy and reliable choice for anyone looking for practical transportation. It's a great opportunity to own a functional car that still has plenty of life left to give!",
